Southtrust to buy 12 Fla branches . SouthTrust Corp and Home Savings of America , a subsidiary of H . F . Ahmanson & Co , said on Tuesday that they have signed a definitive agreement for the purchase of 12 Savings of America branches by SouthTrust Bank of Florida , N . A . The branches , with $ 974 million in deposits , are located on the west coast of Florida . Home Savings of America said that the sale of the branches is part of its ongoing efforts to consolidate its deposit - gathering activities . The sale , which is subject to certain conditions and regulatory approvals , has been scheduled to be completed during the second quarter of 1997 . SouthTrust Bank of Florida N . A . , currently operates 157 banking locations in Florida with total assets of more than $ 5 billion as of December 31 , 1996 . ( ( New York Newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 ) ) 
